{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>An Ever-changing World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Svarog's Dream, the absolute freedom to explore the world and make decisions is yours. However, every action influences the world around you, for better or worse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Soul Lost Between Worlds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You start as a lost soul, inhabiting human hosts who are desperate enough to embrace you. With each death, you revisit the underworld to possess a new body from a selection of unique characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Pawn in the Game of Gods</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While humans wage their wars on Earth, the Gods clash against each other in the sky.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even with their immense power, they search for a means to gain momentum in their eternal battles. All existence is bound by the threads of destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Except for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have the power of free will, a gift the gods will go to great lengths to persuade to their side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004640/extras/p10.png?t=1736417374\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The old prophecy:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;Svarog, the first god, created six worlds and fell asleep.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>In his dream, he created the seventh world, Earth.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Once he wakes up, Earth will cease to exist.&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Immersive Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embrace a living, responsive world filled with emergent stories, while also experiencing over 100 handcrafted quests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Eat, cook, sleep, craft potions, upgrade gear, buy houses, take loans, and even evade debt collectors or headhunters, among much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create your own character build using abilities from 12 unique classes, and equip them with hundreds of weapons, armor pieces, and accessories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004640/extras/m7.png?t=1736417374\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;We took everything we loved about old-school RPGs and then added a modern twist on top of it all.&quot;</i></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Dajbog's Blessing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2004640/b84f49813de5f5b570a6fb9bdc0ead77e70e858b.jpg"},{"name":"Perun's Blessing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2004640/91383e9ad9323095fdbbba4fdff17f4bcbe3cd26.jpg"},{"name":"Mokosh Blessing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2004640/9bc533af81faddb2293b855f2e4d8aae80979ec5.jpg"},{"name":"Morana's Blessing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2004640/4a6143d635b4e7190214f3b8e9b5a01a182d6a90.jpg"},{"name":"Veles Blessing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2004640/8f247544f1132624d304a6e83dcad521adea55a4.jpg"},{"name":"World Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2004640/70f994d141934f3a1908f4977c2cf8d4eea9c438.jpg"},{"name":"Veles Path","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2004640/45326be74af0714e9c5f602f0490b3b83e771b2d.jpg"},{"name":"Peruns Way","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2004640/aac1512e627daa73ecbedb7af22c5df565fcfef6.jpg"},{"name":"Eternal Sleep","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2004640/312cffd3922bb3